entries.quest_destroy_d: In an effort to cripple the Hidden Daggers, destroy five of their Leaders.
entries.quest_location_d: The Hidden Daggers tend to hunt in the Corellia system.  Go there to kill their leaders.
entries.split_quest_alert: You should not let them get the better of you.  Go back out there do your duty!
entries.title: Corellia System: Seek and Destroy 5 Hidden Dagger Leaders.
entries.title_d: Travel to the Corellia system, hunt down, and destroy five Hidden Dagger Leaders. You will receive navigational points of common Hidden Dagger activity. When you complete this mission, return to Acun Solari in Tyrena on Corellia.
